		<p class="standout secondary">I'm here because of people like you.</p>
		<p class="standout secondary">Who are you, exactly? You’re the sort of person who gets things done. Who organises teams, who plans and calculates things that improve the world. You’re a producer, a visionary, a renegade. And, if you’re reading this, you have a product I want to be a part of.</p>
